<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Terms - OWCS Tipping</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/global.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/layout.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/components.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/interactive.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/match-cards.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/pages/info.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main class="page-shell">
    <section class="page-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Terms</h1>
        <hr>
        <p>
          Basic terms for using the OWCS Tipping platform responsibly and fairly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-content">
      <div class="container info-layout">
        <div>
          <h2>Use of the Site</h2>
          <hr>
          <p>
            By using this platform, you agree to use it in good faith and in a way that does not disrupt,
            exploit, or unfairly affect other users or the operation of the site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>Accounts</h2>
          <hr>
          <p>
            Users are responsible for maintaining the security of their own account details. You must not
            share your account or attempt to access another user’s account without permission.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>Tipping and Credits</h2>
          <hr>
          <p>
            Credits and odds on this platform are part of an internal site system only. They do not represent
            real money, financial value, or gambling services. Tips, rankings, and credit values may be adjusted
            if bugs, incorrect data, or abuse are identified.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>Fair Use</h2>
          <hr>
          <p>
            You must not attempt to abuse the platform through cheating, automation, exploitation of bugs,
            manipulation of data, or creation of multiple accounts for unfair advantage.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div >
          <h2>Site Changes</h2>
          <hr>
          <p>
            Features, pages, scoring behaviour, and data structures may change over time as the project evolves.
            Access to parts of the site may also be updated, restricted, or removed where necessary.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>Administration</h2>
          <hr>
          <p>
            Site administrators may take reasonable action to maintain fairness, resolve issues, correct errors,
            and protect the integrity of the platform. This may include adjusting credits, tips, or account access
            where necessary.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>No Official Affiliation</h2>
          <hr>
          <p>
            Use of this site does not imply any official relationship with the Overwatch Champions Series or
            Blizzard Entertainment. Please refer to the Disclaimer page for more information.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>